{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/ghibli-isao-takahata-meninggal/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Sutradara Ghibli Isao Takahata Meninggal Dunia","content":"<p>Komunitas animasi dan animator dunia kembali berduka. Salah satu sosok berpengaruh dalam dunia animasi telah meninggal dunia. Beliau adalah Isao Takahata, seorang sutradara dan salah satu pendiri <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/q-studio-ghibli-transfer-knowledge-film-baru-sampai-disney/\">Studio Ghibli</a>.</p>\n<p>Dilaporkan, Takahata meninggal di usia 82 tahun. Menurut sumber anonim, kesehatan Takahata sudah menurun sejak satu tahun terakhir. Beliau menghembuskan nafas terakhirnya pada hari Kamis di sebuah rumah sakit di Tokyo.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_45680\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-45680\" data-attachment-id=\"45680\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/ghibli-isao-takahata-meninggal/attachment/01-isao-takahata/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/01-isao-takahata.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"01-isao-takahata\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/01-isao-takahata-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/01-isao-takahata.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-45680\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/01-isao-takahata.jpg\" alt=\"01-isao-takahata\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/01-isao-takahata.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/01-isao-takahata-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-45680\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Tiga besar Ghibli: Hayao Miyazaki, Toshio Suzuki, dan Isao Takahata, (Sumber: A113Animation)</p></div></p>\n<p>Semasa hidupnya, Isao Takahata dikenal sebagai salah satu tokoh penting dalam Studio Ghibli, selain sutradara kenamaan Hayao Miyazaki. Semasa hidupnya, Takahata telah menyutradarai berbagai judul <em>anime</em> klasik; entah itu untuk siaran TV atau film bioskop. Judul-judul seperti Heidi, Anne of Green Gables, Secret Akko-chan, Only Yesterday, dan masih banyak lagi.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_45681\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-45681\" data-attachment-id=\"45681\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/ghibli-isao-takahata-meninggal/attachment/02-isao-takahata/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/02-isao-takahata.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"02-isao-takahata\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/02-isao-takahata-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/02-isao-takahata.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-45681\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/02-isao-takahata.jpg\" alt=\"02-isao-takahata\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/02-isao-takahata.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/02-isao-takahata-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-45681\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Grave of the Fireflies, bukan untuk yang berhati lemah. (Sumber: Letterboxd)</p></div></p>\n<p>Namun, satu film Takahata yang paling sukses bisa dinobatkan kepada Grave of the Fireflies. Film <em>anime</em> ini mengangkat sisi gelap Perang Dunia II dari sudut pandang dua orang kakak beradik yang masih anak-anak. Bisa dibilang plot yang disajikan cukup depresif, tergantung bagaimana kamu melihatnya.</p>\n<p>Kritikus film Roger Ebert menjadikan Grave of the Fireflies sebagai salah satu film terbaik yang pernah ia tonton. “Ya, film ini memang kartun dan mata karakternya sebesar piring. Meski demikian, film ini pantas masuk ke dalam daftar film perang terbaik yang pernah ada.”</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_45682\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-45682\" data-attachment-id=\"45682\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/ghibli-isao-takahata-meninggal/attachment/03-isao-takahata/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/03-isao-takahata.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"03-isao-takahata\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/03-isao-takahata-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/03-isao-takahata.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-45682\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/03-isao-takahata.jpg\" alt=\"03-isao-takahata\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/03-isao-takahata.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/03-isao-takahata-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-45682\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Roger Ebert memuji Grave of the Fireflies. (Sumber: Medium)</p></div></p>\n<p>Dalam kesempatan yang sama, Ebert juga mengakui ulasan Grave of the Fireflies dari Ernest Rister. Menurutnya, Grave of the Fireflies pantas disandingkan dengan film Schindler’s List dari Steven Spielberg. <em>Anime</em> ini juga merupakan film animasi paling humanis yang pernah ia saksikan.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_45683\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-45683\" data-attachment-id=\"45683\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/ghibli-isao-takahata-meninggal/attachment/04-isao-takahata/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/04-isao-takahata.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"04-isao-takahata\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/04-isao-takahata-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/04-isao-takahata.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-45683\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/04-isao-takahata.jpg\" alt=\"04-isao-takahata\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/04-isao-takahata.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/04-isao-takahata-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-45683\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Setiap frame dalam Princess Kaguya adalah karya seni. (Sumber: Sanctum in Heremis)</p></div></p>\n<p>Film terakhir yang disutradarai Takahata adalah The Tale of the Princess Kaguya di tahun 2013 silam. Film ini mendapatkan nominasi dalam ajang Academy Awards di Amerika. Keunikan dari <em>anime</em> ini adalah presentasi visualnya yang sangat artistik; dengan meniru estetika lukisan klasik Jepang.</p>\n<p>Dalam wawancaranya bersama Variety di tahun 2016, Takahata mengaku masih punya beberapa ide untuk film <em>anime</em> selanjutnya. “Saya punya beberapa proyek di kepala saya yang tengah saya upayakan untuk bisa diproduksi. Apakah nanti akan jadi film atau tidak, tak ada yang tahu, bahkan saya sendiri.”</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_45684\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-45684\" data-attachment-id=\"45684\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/ghibli-isao-takahata-meninggal/attachment/05-isao-takahata/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/05-isao-takahata.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"05-isao-takahata\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/05-isao-takahata-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/05-isao-takahata.jpg\" class=\"wp-image-45684 size-full\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/05-isao-takahata.jpg\" alt=\"05 isao takahata\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/05-isao-takahata.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/05-isao-takahata-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-45684\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Kreator sekaliber Takahata pantas mendapatkan apresiasi tinggi. (Sumber: Culturebox)</p></div></p>\n<p>Pada akhirnya, The Tale of Princess Kaguya memang menjadi film terakhir yang dibuat seorang Isao Takahata. Namun, apa yang telah ia berikan kepada dunia animasi merupakan salah satu mahakarya yang patut mendapatkan penghargaan tertinggi.</p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"6b942bdb-de75-5f14-9bce-46ce16b87975"}}}